## 🔄 Communication Flow Examples

### Example 1: Manual Control Session

```
Phone          Robot
  |              |
  |              |--- RASCAL:READY
  |<-------------|
  |              |
  |--- FWD ------|
  |              |... moves forward
  |              |
  |              |--- STATUS:MANUAL|...
  |<-------------|
