## ⚡ Protocol Specifications

### Timing

| Parameter | Value | Notes |
|-----------|-------|-------|
| Baud Rate | 9600 bps | Both Bluetooth and GPS |
| Command Response | <100ms | Immediate for most commands |
| Status Update Interval | 2000ms | Automatic, every 2 seconds |
| GPS Update Rate | 1000ms | Internal, affects heading calc |
| Command Timeout | N/A | No timeout, last command persists |

### Buffer Sizes

- **Bluetooth Receive Buffer:** 64 bytes (Arduino Serial)
- **Maximum Command Length:** 50 characters
- **Maximum Response Length:** 150 characters

### Error Handling

- **Invalid Command:** Silently ignored (no error message)
- **Malformed GOTO:** Silently ignored
- **GPS Loss During Navigation:** Robot stops, waits for fix
- **Bluetooth Disconnection:** Robot continues last command

