## 🔒 Security Considerations

### Bluetooth Pairing
- **Default PIN:** 1234 or 0000 (HC-05 default)
- **Recommendation:** Change PIN in HC-05 AT mode
- **Range:** ~10 meters (line of sight)

### Command Validation
- No authentication in current protocol
- Any paired device can send commands
- **Future Enhancement:** Add command authentication

