## 🔍 Debugging Protocol

### Enable Serial Monitor
Connect Arduino via USB (with battery OFF) and open Serial Monitor (9600 baud)

### What You'll See:
```
RASCAL Autonomous Delivery Robot
Initializing...
Waiting for GPS fix...
BT Command: FWD
Distance: 15.3m, Bearing: 32.5°, Heading: 28.1°, Error: 4.4°
Waypoint reached!
```

### Common Debug Messages:
- `BT Command: [cmd]` - Command received
- `Waypoint set: [lat], [lon]` - Navigation started
- `Distance: [dist]m` - Waypoint distance calculated
- `Bearing: [deg]°` - Direction to target
- `Heading: [deg]°` - Robot's current heading

